3.2 VULNERABILITY OVERVIEW
3.2.1 ‚ÄãALLOCATION OF RESOURCES WITHOUT LIMITS OR THROTTLING CWE-770
‚ÄãThe affected devices‚Äô web server contains a vulnerability that could lead to a denial-of-service condition. An attacker could cause total loss of web server availability, which could recover after the attack.
‚ÄãCVE-2023-39269 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 7.5 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:H).
